{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-381-prime-k-factorial","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 381: faktorijal od (broj sa bazom k)","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kwa namba msingi $p$ acheni $S(p) = (\\sum (p - k)!)\\bmod (p)$ kwa $1 ≤ k ≤ 5$.</p>\n<p>Kwa mfano, ikiwa $p = 7$,</p>\n<p>$$(7 - 1)! + (7 - 2)! + (7 - 3)! + (7 - 4)! + (7 - 5)! = 6! + 5! + 4! + 3! + 2! = 720 + 120 + 24 + 6 + 2 = 872$$</p>\n<p>Kwa kuwa $872\\bmod (7) = 4$, basi $S(7) = 4$.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da $\\sum S(p) = 480$ za $5 ≤ p &#x3C; 100$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum S(p)$ za $5 ≤ p &#x3C; {10}^8$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4ea1000cf542c50fffc","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302045,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-381-prime-k-factorial"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function primeKFactorial() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nprimeKFactorial();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>primeKFactorial()</code> treba da vrati <code>139602943319822</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(primeKFactorial(), 139602943319822);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-381-prime-k-factorial","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstSt